<dl id="n38146c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n38" href="#n38146c">N38 (VI.B.32)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n38all.htm#n38146c"> 146(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> down with / homofun</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">We should <mark>eliminate homophones</mark>. It is true that in so doing we shall deny ourselves the pleasure of the pun, but we shall no doubt find other pleasures to compensate for this loss. <small> Sir Richard Paget, <a name="RPBP" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#RPBP"><cite title="source">Babel, or The Past, Present and Future of Human Speech</cite></a> (1930) 85</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
